      "text": "You never run and you know now you hear it get a level when you hear it in the show",
      "start": 30
    },
    {
      "end": 38.220001220703125,
      "text": "And you know you just jumpin' man where do you go?",
      "start": 34.79999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 41.720001220703125,
      "text": "Mario, Chico, got the wall whistle come on",
      "start": 38.47999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 44.34000015258789,
      "text": "Woo woo woo got the wall whistle come on",
